Step 4. We calculate the gradient and take a step downhill.

12
00:00:57,533 --> 00:01:02,977
Step 5. We calculate the gradient and take a step downhill.

13
00:01:04,133 --> 00:01:07,114
We continue this process, taking smaller and

14
00:01:07,214 --> 00:01:09,985
